<p><a href="https://github.com/Amegma/Galaxy-Attack"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ae/Github-desktop-logo-symbol.svg" width="22" height="22" /> GitHub Repo</a></p>

<p>This project comes under an open-source gaming organization called <a href="https://github.com/Amegma">Amegma</a>, and it is an inspiration of an arcade game which was Atari Space Invaders</p>

<p><a href="https://youtu.be/ejA89NtTH2k">Demo Game Video</a></p>

<h2 id="technologies-used">Technologies Used</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Python</li>
  <li>Framework - PyGame</li>
  <li>Other modules - time, os, sys, ctypes, etc.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="guidelines-to-setup">Guidelines to setup</h2>

<h3 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Python should be installed: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Python version &gt; 3.10</code></li>
  <li>Pygame should be installed: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Pygame version &gt; 1.9.5</code></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="run-the-game">Run the game</h3>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><!-- <td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
</pre></td> --><td class="rouge-code"><pre>python &lt;file_path&gt;/main.py
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="create-a-release">Create a release</h3>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><!-- <td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
